This paper discusses the challenges and solutions for implementing federated machine learning in coalition settings, which involves sharing data and models across multiple partners while maintaining privacy and security. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
